snippet.title: Ganz Launches Webkinz Friends Game on Facebook
snippet.description:
Visit us: http://www.webkinzinsider.com

Ganz has launched an all-new Webkinz game on Facebook called Webkinz Friends. It's still in beta and hasn't been officially launched yet, but it looks like a very polished new game that offers gameplay that the original Webkinz World simply cannot. Think of it as Webkinz World 2.0!
